Tranquil retreat
Nature and serenity await you

Misty Dews offers serene accommodation nestled in lush greenery, with breathtaking river views that captivate the soul. Located near the Check Dam and just 9 km from the Ancient Jain Temple, this homestay is a haven for peace seekers and nature lovers. Enjoy your private balcony, relax on the terrace, and take advantage of free private parking. Explore nearby attractions like the Heritage Museum, Edakkal Caves, and Neelimala Viewpoint, all while immersing yourself in the beauty of Kannur.
